title: february 16: somebody call 911
description:
Today on 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the town that launched the first 911 emergency phone system in America. Then, Maia talks about how Lady GaGa's "Born This Way" made history by rocketing to the top of the charts to become the Billboard Hot 100's 1000th number one hit. Join this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
